- `/src/services/flight-memory/index.js` - Memory system integration
- `/src/services/video-system/index.js` - Video generation capabilities

## 7. Video System Integration

RIX/CRX agents have direct integration with the Video System, providing:

- Green screen technology for agent visualization
- Google Video Generation API integration
- Real-time video composition and editing
- Custom background generation and application

These capabilities allow agents to create visual content for presentations, tutorials, and interactive sessions.

## 8. Command Line Interface

The Aixtiv CLI provides comprehensive tools for managing RIX/CRX entities:

```bash
